|text1     = When a character receives a killing blow in combat, they will {{Color|h|nobold=1|not be knocked down}} and will immediately recover some HP.
|image2    = Tutorial Combat Countdown Penalty 2.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_10001602.png>-<Tutorial Combat Countdown Penalty 2.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text2     = When a character takes a killing blow in combat, the battle {{Color|h|nobold=1|countdown timer}} will decrease, causing the {{Color|h|nobold=1|combat to end early}}.<br />This means it will be {{Color|h|nobold=1|harder}} to {{Color|h|nobold=1|defeat all enemies}} before the countdown expires.
