|text3     = Please improve your {{Color|h|nobold=1|team's survivability}} by finding suitable {{Color|h|nobold=1|healer characters}}, {{Color|h|nobold=1|Bonds}}, or {{Color|h|nobold=1|sustain equipment}} to avoid combat ending prematurely.
